Maintainer: Alexander Wireko Kena <alex.kena24@gmail.com>
Description: A no-frills open-source solution for designing experimental or trial plot labels affixed with QR codes.
    It features 'EasyQrlabelr', a Shiny app that simplifies the complicated process of 
    plot label design for non-R users. 
